Brent Crude Oil (BOOY) Opening Price Probability Distribution Analysis
Overview
This repository contains Monte Carlo pressure test models and probability distribution analysis for the March 30, 2026 (Monday) opening price of Brent Crude Oil (BOOY). The analysis evaluates market resilience, supply shock risks, and price projection scenarios under current geopolitical tensions in the Middle East.
Core Parameters & Scenarios
All scenarios are calibrated with a spot anchor price of $106.09 (previous close) and simulate geopolitical supply shocks, physical market gaps, and global buffer capacity.
